title: first-website
text:
mtcars |>
select(mpg, wt) |>
ggplot(aes(x = wt, y = mpg)) +
geom_point() +
geom_smooth(method = "lm", formula = y ~ x, se = FALSE) +
theme_clean() +
labs(title = "Fuel Efficiency and Weight", subtitle = "Heavier cars are less efficient",
  x = "Weight (1000s of lbs)", y = "MPG", 
  caption = "Henderson and Vellerman (1981)")
